                        <interp inst="t18371211-name-218" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN HARRISON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable E</hi> 150.) I took the prisoner into custody, and took him to the Mary-le-bone station-house.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
